**Abstract:**
Summer research grant report (NEH) on Chantilly project. Describes progress on collecting medieval sources at Centre Culturel "Les Fontaines" and writing persuasive account of medieval theologians' objections to applying Aristotelian science to theology. Reports two substantive paper drafts in progress on biblical narrative vs. Aristotelian scientific model. Notes difficulty explaining connection between adoption of Aristotelian conception and loss of narrative understanding.

